537
00:38:44,553 --> 00:38:47,657
♪I look at your back♪

538
00:38:47,657 --> 00:38:50,025
♪But I'm powerless♪

539
00:38:50,025 --> 00:38:53,673
♪It seems you're going to give up on me♪

540
00:38:54,271 --> 00:38:57,801
♪I'm behind you, slowly following you♪

541
00:38:57,801 --> 00:39:01,587
♪Until the sun sets♪

542
00:39:01,587 --> 00:39:03,721
♪When will you stop♪

543
00:39:03,721 --> 00:39:05,481
♪To admire the scenery with me♪

544
00:39:05,481 --> 00:39:08,361
♪Do you know it all doesn't come easy♪

545
00:39:08,361 --> 00:39:11,881
♪I'm behind you, slowly following you♪

546
00:39:11,881 --> 00:39:17,385
♪Following until the moon
wakes up the dawn♪

547
00:39:17,385 --> 00:39:19,401
♪If you can't remember♪

548
00:39:19,401 --> 00:39:21,609
♪I can help you recall♪

549
00:39:21,609 --> 00:39:23,689
♪Reviewing on the one hand♪

550
00:39:24,201 --> 00:39:30,633
♪Picking up on the other♪
